cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SI, cs.SY 

The paper presents a machine learning approach to predict electricity consumption using deep recurrent neural networks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
